  "description": "Night music. Dark vowel space (O/U), low filter, gentle resonance that adds just enough nasal quality to suggest a voice humming in the dark. Minimal drama — partials drift independently like stars. Slow LFO on resonance sensitivity means occasional harmonic constellations form and dissolve.",
